'''Leatheris''' was a type of [[Leather/Legends|leather]] that was used to make clothing. [[Trever Flume]] offered to sell some to [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] to replace his tattered [[Jedi apparel/Legends|Jedi robes]]. Later it was revealed that he had stolen it from [[Mariana's Exquisite Designs and Alterations]] just before.

